You remain in complete control throughout this experience.<break time="2s"/>
At any time,<break time="1s"/> you can return to full waking awareness<break time="1.5s"/> simply by opening your eyes.<break time="2.5s"/>

This journey is safe.<break time="2s"/>
This journey is yours.<break time="2.5s"/>

So find a comfortable position now.<break time="2s"/>
Sitting or lying down,<break time="1.5s"/> wherever you feel most at ease.<break time="2.5s"/>
Allow your body to be fully supported.<break time="2s"/>
And when you are ready,<break time="1.5s"/> in your own time,<break time="1s"/> allow your eyes to gently close.<break time="4s"/>
</prosody>

